{
  "chapter": 75,
  "chapter_summary": "第75章讲述了燕南天（实为路仲远冒充）与魏白衣的激战。燕南天击败魏白衣后，江玉郎假冒武当弟子接近，趁燕南天为慕容九妹疗伤时暗算得手。铁萍姑虽恨江玉郎，却在他求饶时心软，助其逃离。江小鱼与花无缺赶到客栈，发现重伤的燕南天。临终前，燕南天揭示自己实为路仲远，受燕南天所托冒充其名震慑江湖。小鱼儿凭智慧识破伪装，路仲远告知燕南天传授武功、借名号震慑恶人的真相。章节以路仲远弥留之际，小鱼儿追问燕南天下落结束，展现了江湖中的恩怨情仇与智谋较量。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bai_yi",
      "speaker_name": "魏白衣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁敢对无牙门下如此无礼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_wei_bai_yi",
      "text": "你是魏无牙的什么人？他现在哪里？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bai_yi",
      "speaker_name": "魏白衣",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "你用不着去找家师，无牙门下的四大弟子，每一个都早已想找燕南天较量较量了，不想我魏白衣运气竟比别人好……",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_wei_bai_yi",
      "text": "你是什么东西，竟敢对燕大侠如此无礼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bai_yi",
      "speaker_name": "魏白衣",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你也敢来和我动手。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_wei_bai_yi",
      "text": "魏无牙在哪里？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_bai_yi",
      "speaker_name": "魏白衣",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "无牙门下士，可杀不可辱……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到魏无牙门下，又多了这些狠毒疯狂的弟子……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但你……你可是武当门下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "武当门下弟子江玉郎，参见燕老前辈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好，好，正派门下有你这样的后起之秀，他们就算再多收几个疯子，我也用不着发愁了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "但今日若非前辈恰巧赶来，弟子哪里还有命在？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这实在巧得很，我若非约好个小朋友在此相见，也不会到这里来的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "他叫花无缺，你近年若常在江湖走动，就该听见过这个名字。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "晚辈下山并没有多久，对江湖侠踪，还生疏得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "弟子方才来到时，那魏白衣要对一位慕容姑娘下手，这位姑娘此刻还躺在屋里，前辈是否要去瞧瞧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "慕容姑娘？……莫非是慕容家的人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这孩子是被他点着哑穴了，这穴道虽非要穴，但因下手太重，而且已点了她至少有六七个时辰。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "已有六七个时辰了么？如此说来，这位姑娘元气必然要亏损很大了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，她气血俱已受损甚巨，我此刻若骤然解开她穴道，她只怕就要等三个月才能恢复过来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "那……那怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我行功为她活血时，最忌有人打扰，若是中断下来，她非但受损更大，我也难免要吃些亏的，但有你在旁守护着，我就用不着担心了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "前辈只管放心，弟子虽无能，如此小事自信还不致有了差错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我若不放心你，还会冒这个险么？……紫髯老道的徒弟，我再不放心还能放心谁？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你又说错了，我不是不愿见他，只不过是‘现在’不愿见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你怎么知道他一定会阻拦你？也许……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "当然他也许会让我去的，但我却不愿冒这个险，这件事我既已决定要做，就非做不可！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "但你既已陪我来到这里……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "燕大侠会在什么地方等你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "就在前面小镇上的一家客栈里。这小镇只有一家客栈，我绝不会找错地方的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我本来想要你陪我到龟山去的，但我知道你既然约了别人，就决不会失信，是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你我今日一别，就不知……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "无论如何，你我总有再见的时候……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "现在时候还早，我也送你一程。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "江玉郎，你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "鼠辈，我救了你性命，你竟敢暗算于我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你究竟是什么人？为何要暗算我？说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要知道我是谁么？好！我告诉你，我就是江南大侠的少爷江玉郎！什么武当弟子，在我眼中简直不值一个屁！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天（路仲远）",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好！好！某家纵横天下，想不到今日竟死在你这贱奴的鼠子手上！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "你既出言不逊，少爷我就要令你在死前还要多受些罪了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "他现在已经快死了，你何必再下毒手。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "好，你叫我饶了他，我就饶了他……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "花无缺就要来了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你已瞧见了他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "还有江小鱼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你说你见到了花无缺，你怎会认得他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "只因我也是移花宫门下……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天（路仲远）",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你……你们来了……很好……很好……",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "晚辈来迟了一步！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天（路仲远）",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我死前能见到你们，死也无憾了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "你不会死的，没有人能杀得死你！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "是谁下的毒手？是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天（路仲远）",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "江玉郎。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我一定要杀了他，为你复仇！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "用不着他去杀江玉郎，江玉郎是我的，无论前辈你是什么人，我都会不顾一切，为前辈复仇的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "无论前辈是什么人？……前辈不是燕大侠是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天（路仲远）",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我自以为能瞒过了所有的人，谁知终于还是没有瞒过你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "前辈难道竟不是燕南天燕大侠？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天（路仲远）",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "燕南天只是我平生第一好友……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "那么前辈你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "路仲远",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我姓路。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "路仲远？前辈莫非是‘南天大侠’路仲远。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "路仲远",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你听过我的名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "弟子五岁时便听过前辈的侠名了，那‘血手’杜杀，虽然几乎死在前辈手中，但对前辈却始终佩服得很。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "但……但路大侠为何要冒燕大侠之名呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "路仲远",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "只……只因燕……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "此事我已猜出一二，不如由我替路大侠来说吧！若是我说的不错，前辈就点点头，若是我说错了，前辈不妨再自己说。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "路仲远",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "燕大侠自‘恶人谷’逃出后，神智虽已渐渐清醒，但武功一时还不能完全恢复，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "路仲远",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "他出谷之后，便找到了路大侠，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "在一路上，他已发现江湖中有大乱将生，只恨自己无力阻止，于是他便想求路大侠助他一臂之力，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "路仲远",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "他又生怕自己武功失传，是以一见路大侠，便将武功秘诀相赠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "路仲远",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我十多年之前，曾受挫于魏无牙之手，那时我才发觉自己武功不足，是以洗手归隐……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "是以这次燕大侠求前辈重出，前辈便生怕自己武功仍有不足，便要燕大侠将自己的武功秘诀相授，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "路大侠就为了这缘故，又不愿掠人之美，所以此番重出江湖，便借了燕大侠的名号。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "以路大侠的身份地位，自然不愿用燕南天的武功，来增加‘南天大侠’的声名，不知弟子猜得可对么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "路仲远",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "除此之外，还有一点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "莫非是燕大侠算定自己一离开‘恶人谷’后，‘恶人谷’的恶人便要倾巢而出，他更怕这些人在江湖中为非作歹，知道这些人惟有‘燕南天’三个字才能震慑得住，所以便求前辈暂时冒充一番。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "路仲远",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你果然是个聪明人，但……但我……我自信不但已学会了燕南天的武功，而且还请万春流将我的面容改变了许多，对于燕南天的音容笑貌，我自信也学得不差，我实在不懂怎么会被你瞧破了？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "前辈一见着我时，本该立刻提起万春流的，但前辈却似完全忘记了这个人，是以那时我已开始怀疑了。而且前辈的神情，却仍和十余年前传说中的燕大侠完全一样，这不但已超出人情之常，而且简直是不可能的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "路仲远",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不错，燕南天的……的确已改变了许多。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "江小鱼",
      "listener": "char_lu_zhong_yuan",
      "text": "现在我只求前辈告诉我，燕大侠，燕伯父，现在究竟是在哪里？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 75,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    }
